  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the tagine pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the chopped carrots and zucchini and cook until they are tender.",
    "Add the sweet chilli sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Add the pasta to the tagine pot and stir to combine with the sauce and vegetables.",
    "Add the pasta water to the tagine pot and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let it cook for 10 minutes or until the pasta is al dente.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy."
